  "1733250": {
    "name": "极爆少年",
    "steam_appid": 1733250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款充满怀旧情怀的类银河战士恶魔城游戏，配备疯狂武器、技能和像素爆浆效果。骑上你的BMX特技单车，在探索废土秘密的同时轰爆你的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/582df1360c158898f2fbe113dfa59fc2.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/e88fc24b97ae2cf36b6b3c56a682862b.poster.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/e88fc24b97ae2cf36b6b3c56a682862b.webm?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/e88fc24b97ae2cf36b6b3c56a682862b.mp4?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一位孤胆战士，踏上横越废土的旅程。这片荒芜废土充斥着恶棍和怪人，你必须彻底消灭他们才能生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/05e7a519d0b00ce0d2ce4bc864d390b0.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/c3bef59aa36cbdba1ab0162757b10b31.poster.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/c3bef59aa36cbdba1ab0162757b10b31.webm?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/c3bef59aa36cbdba1ab0162757b10b31.mp4?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奔跑、爬行、跳跃、攀爬，还有在类银河战士恶魔城游戏中前所未有的创举（但大可不必去查证这点）——骑单车穿越世界！女士们先生们，我们为您呈现人力交通科技的巅峰之作：全地形单车！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你那可靠的BMX极限单车随时一键可召。更快速地穿梭地图，进入新区域，将单车掷向敌人，还能表演酷炫的单车特技来获得奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/e7d9df93c6fef33a412b9ddd2c0d91b0.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/808656877f892734373b83cc4c4f797a.poster.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/808656877f892734373b83cc4c4f797a.webm?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/808656877f892734373b83cc4c4f797a.mp4?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用必备的砍刀劈砍敌人，或者用极爆小子那充满混乱能量的涡轮手套™射击他们。涡轮爆破、电击、圆锯片……利用你手头的各种武器来斩杀、撕裂或炸飞敌人，制造出疯狂戏剧化的像素血浆爆炸特效！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/1849568dc8873dadb2296f9c00d4e464.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/013fa667121d658449df65a782dc3d3a.poster.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/013fa667121d658449df65a782dc3d3a.webm?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/013fa667121d658449df65a782dc3d3a.mp4?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事紧接着《极爆少年》的电影结局展开 - 在你的旅程中，你将遇到各种怪咖和异类角色，有朋友，有敌人，还有游荡于两者之间的人物。他们会提供建议、任务、战斗和笑话（非常多的笑话），共同构成一个温情且荒诞的故事——该故事是与电影原班制作人合作创作的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索不同区域，按照你认为合适的顺序击败各个Boss，做出影响剧情走向的选择，让你可以通过多次游玩体验不同的路线和结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/3a9cc535066194e672fcd166925f4cc6.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/e5290026c3aee2aeee774ad351c1a7c1.poster.avif?t=1754510951\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/e5290026c3aee2aeee774ad351c1a7c1.webm?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733250/extras/e5290026c3aee2aeee774ad351c1a7c1.mp4?t=1754510951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你不关心剧情，只对游戏玩法感兴趣（速通爱好者们，我们说的就是你们），所有对话都可以跳过。如果你不想参与，许多过场动画也可以直接略过。</p>",
